x^TA{\dot x}
(x^TA{\dot x})^T = x^TA{\dot x}
({\dot x}^TAx)^T ={\dot x}^TAx
(x^TA{\dot x})^T = {\dot x}^TA^Tx
x^TA{\dot x} = {\dot x}^TA^Tx
x^TA{\dot x} + {\dot x}^TAx = {\dot x}^TA^Tx + {\dot x}^TAx = {\dot x}^T(A^T + A)x. \tag{1}
A^T = A
x^TA{\dot x} + {\dot x}^TAx = 2{\dot x} ^TAx; \tag{2}
